## User Story

As a **user**, I want to **register and log in to my account**, so that I can securely manage my preferences and data.

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 1**: Users should be able to register with an email and password.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 2**: Users should be able to log in with their credentials.
- [ ] **Acceptance Criteria 3**: Display error messages for invalid login attempts.

## Tasks

- [ ] **Task 1**: Set up authentication routes in the back-end.
- [ ] **Task 2**: Create registration and login forms on the front-end.
- [ ] **Task 3**: Implement JWT token-based authentication.

## Additional Information

- **Priority**: High
- **Related Issues**: #103
- **Dependencies**: None

## Notes

Use bcrypt for password hashing and JWT for user sessions.
